<body>

    <!--Navigation Bar -->
    <%- include("../components/navigation-bar") %>


    <!--Header video -->
    <header>
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <video playsinline="playsinline" autobuffer="true" autoplay="true" loop="true" muted="muted">
            <source src="media/indexvideo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
        <div class="container h-100">
            <div class="d-flex h-100 text-center align-items-center">
                <div class="w-100 text-white">
                    <h1 class="display-3">Projects Nest</h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-0">Get a developer to create your project or create one for someone else!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="section-1">
        <section class="timeline">
            <p class="lead align sect1txt">For the developer</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-left" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#1</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Create an account or login to an existing one!</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-right" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#2</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Find an available project that you like and you have the skills to do! </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-left" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#3</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Get in contact with the customer who posted the project and make a conversation about the
                            requirements for both ends.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-right" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#4</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Complete the project but always communicate with the customer to fill you up with the details
                            of their needs. </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-left" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#5</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Mark the project as finished and wait for the customer for confirmation.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-right" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#6</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Get paid for your work and start looking for your next amazing project!</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

    </section>

    <section class="section-2">
        <div class="timeline">
            <p class="lead align sect2txt">For the customer</p>
            <ul style="background:linear-gradient(#112d4e,#405671)">
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-left" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#1</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Create an account or login to an existing one!</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-right" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#2</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Think of an idea and plan in out in your amazing brain of yours! </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-left" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#3</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Post about the project that you want to be completed by a professional developer and its
                            requirements!</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-right" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#4</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Reach to a developer or wait for a developer to contact you.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-left" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#5</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>Assign your project to a developer that fulfills all your requirements and needs and wait for
                            the project to be completed.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div data-aos="fade-right" class="content">
                        <h2>
                            <time>#6</time>
                        </h2>
                        <p>When the project is marked as completed see it by yourself, make some adjustments if needed,
                            pay the developer and enjoy your idea in action! </p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

